{"tid":1248344,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"討論下: 關於係日本工作既中國人???","createTime":"2019-06-21T12:14:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T01:12:24.000Z","uid":162409,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"482236d08ead65d205913ed2fee361d6daf1f8e2","tid":1248344,"uid":162409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:14:06.000Z","msg":"旅行時去一d 秋葉原商場, 各大藥妝店等<br />\n都遇到有幾多中國人做售貨員, 收銀員<br />\n因為佢地個名牌有支那旗<br />\n<br />\n問題係應該唔會全部都係留學生掛?<br />\n乜大陸人有日本工作假期咩?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3791a75939737173a7a35539a85533c1da2c911f","tid":1248344,"uid":20429,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:15:00.000Z","msg":"不嬲大陸人係好有辦法周圍移民<br />\n唔係點會叫蝗蟲"},{"pid":"d5d3c5dc656b392b7d1c14c10453209898324b73","tid":1248344,"uid":162409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:24:03.000Z","msg":"另外都見唔少越南 泰國 黎巴嫩  <br />\n有遇過做飲食店waiter 又有酒店執房<br />\n<br />\n正常屋企有一百幾十萬供去日本讀幾年書都唔會番呢d工啦<br />\n究竟係咩玩法?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好奇佢地揸咩visa去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"070db7654f8937920dfa70ea2718685b3026ec56","tid":1248344,"uid":29052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d5d3c5dc656b392b7d1c14c10453209898324b73","tid":1248344,"uid":162409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:24:03.000Z","msg":"另外都見唔少越南 泰國 黎巴嫩  <br />\n有遇過做飲食店waiter 又有酒店執房<br />\n<br />\n正常屋企有一百幾十萬供去日本讀幾年書都唔會番呢d工啦<br />\n究竟係咩玩法?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好奇佢地揸咩visa去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:27:27.000Z","msg":"多數留學生<br />\n錯啦，大陸學生去得日本讀多數中產<br />\n好有錢既人唔會好多，只少我無見過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋人工好高藥局，1個鐘1000&yen;-1200&yen; 不等<br />\n仲多數包車錢。同埋佢地大陸人都係請黎招呼自己友。打依啲荀工有咩所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cda1d679909283f994d04ff8a35e7b596d62d3b9","tid":1248344,"uid":16270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d5d3c5dc656b392b7d1c14c10453209898324b73","tid":1248344,"uid":162409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:24:03.000Z","msg":"另外都見唔少越南 泰國 黎巴嫩  <br />\n有遇過做飲食店waiter 又有酒店執房<br />\n<br />\n正常屋企有一百幾十萬供去日本讀幾年書都唔會番呢d工啦<br />\n究竟係咩玩法?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好奇佢地揸咩visa去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:27:48.000Z","msg":"咪日本既working holiday.點解一定要掛勾讀緊書"},{"pid":"1f04e1c41847d8135c41e77ed0fa3265feeb7b5f","tid":1248344,"uid":29052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:29:08.000Z","msg":"加上有得揀我請願返藥局。<br />\n又唔辛苦，又唔洗點對日本客（日本都唔少閪客）<br />\n人工又高。"},{"pid":"7db83da4c75c7cabf865a5abc91cad07ad22bf32","tid":1248344,"uid":162409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3791a75939737173a7a35539a85533c1da2c911f","tid":1248344,"uid":20429,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:15:00.000Z","msg":"不嬲大陸人係好有辦法周圍移民<br />\n唔係點會叫蝗蟲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:29:09.000Z","msg":"只係覺得有古惑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好容易正規就去到香港人仲唔9衝"},{"pid":"721d18f3cee69a46685ad4d9f50d35a13a78ea0a","tid":1248344,"uid":162409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cda1d679909283f994d04ff8a35e7b596d62d3b9","tid":1248344,"uid":16270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d5d3c5dc656b392b7d1c14c10453209898324b73","tid":1248344,"uid":162409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:24:03.000Z","msg":"另外都見唔少越南 泰國 黎巴嫩  <br />\n有遇過做飲食店waiter 又有酒店執房<br />\n<br />\n正常屋企有一百幾十萬供去日本讀幾年書都唔會番呢d工啦<br />\n究竟係咩玩法?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好奇佢地揸咩visa去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hk